## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-523"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>類別中已過時[!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-523">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-524">您可以建立對其進行驗證<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>所使用的執行個體<xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings>類別和<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-524">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-525">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 參考頁面的＜備註＞一節。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-525">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-526">使用這個方法之後呼叫<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.MoveToAttribute%2A>閱讀組成屬性值的文字或實體參考節點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-526">Use this method after calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.MoveToAttribute%2A> to read through the text or entity reference nodes that make up the attribute value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-527"><xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Depth%2A>的屬性值節點是一個加上該屬性節點的深度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-527">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Depth%2A> of the attribute value nodes is one plus the depth of the attribute node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-528">`Depth`遞增和遞減 1 當您逐步執行和跳離一般實體參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-528">The `Depth` increments and decrements by one when you step into and out of general entity references.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-529">例如，假設您有下列的 XML: `<test name="a &b; c"/>`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-529">For example, suppose you have the following XML: `<test name="a &b; c"/>`</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-530">其中實體`b`定義文件類型定義 (DTD) 中，如下所示： `<!ENTITY b "123">`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-530">where the entity `b` is defined in the document type definition (DTD) as follows: `<!ENTITY b "123">`</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2ca49-531">如果<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.EntityHandling%2A>設`ExpandCharEntities`，下列 C# 程式碼傳回屬性值做為兩個文字節點和一個實體參考節點：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ca49-531">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.EntityHandling%2A> is set to `ExpandCharEntities`, the following C# code returns the attribute value as two text nodes and one entity reference node:</span></span>  

```  
reader.MoveToAttribute("name");  
  while (reader.ReadAttributeValue())  
  {  
  if (reader.NodeType == XmlNodeType.Text)  
  {  
  // at this point reader.Value == "a " or " c"  
  }  
  else if (reader.NodeType == XmlNodeType.EntityReference)  
  {  
  // at this point reader.Name == "b"  
  reader.ResolveEntity();  
  while (reader.ReadAttributeValue() &&  
  reader.NodeType != XmlNodeType.EndEntity)  
  {  
  // reader.Value == "123"  
  }  
  }  
    }  
```  



